text: Jasmine Felicia Crockett (born March 29, 1981) is an American attorney and politician. She is a member of the United States House of Representatives for the Texas's 30th congressional district since 2023. In 2021, she became a member of the Texas House of Representatives from the 100th district. Crockett was named as co-chair of the 2024 Harris-Walz campaign. Crockett is a member of the Congressional Progressive Caucus. ==References== Category:1981 births Category:Living people Category:United States representatives from Texas Category:Politicians from St. Louis, Missouri Category:Lawyers from Texas Category:Lawyers from St. Louis, Missouri Category:Democratic Party (United States) politicians Category:African-American politicians Category:Members of the Texas Legislature
